{
  "id": "adv_event_2112_01_02",
  "title": "秘密の計画",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "小麦粉、卵、砂糖、バター、牛乳……\nうん、材料は全部揃ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wheat flour‚ eggs‚ sugar‚ butter‚ milk…\nRight‚ I’ve got all the ingredients lined up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 10.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "寮のキッチンにオーブンがあるから\nこれでケーキが焼けるはず！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The dorm kitchen has an oven‚\nso I should have everything I need to bake the cake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4333333333,
      "endTime": 15.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "今日は二人の帰りが遅いから\nその間にクリスマスケーキ作りをマスターしないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’ll be coming home late today‚\nso I have to master Christmas cake baking before they do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1333333333,
      "endTime": 22.1878359539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "二人に美味しいって言ってもらえるように頑張るぞ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to do my best‚ so they’ll say it’s delicious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3666666667,
      "endTime": 26.6542176406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Two hours later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.4333333333,
      "endTime": 28.666666666599998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "うう……どうしてうまくいかないんだろ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ohhh… Why isn’t it working…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4666666667,
      "endTime": 33.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "スポンジ生地が膨らまないなぁ……\nレシピ通りなはずなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sponge doesn’t rise…\nI think I did everything like the recipe says…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1,
      "endTime": 39.5268183283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "中心も生焼けで味ももそもそしてて\nお店のケーキみたいにふわふわにならないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The center is under-baked and the flavor is muddy.\nIt’s not fluffy like a cake in a shop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7333333333,
      "endTime": 47.5569841041,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "卵もしっかり泡立てたし、砂糖もちゃんと計ったし\nどこで失敗したのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I beat the egg well‚ and measured the sugar right.\nWhy did it fail?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7666666667,
      "endTime": 55.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "何してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you up to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3,
      "endTime": 56.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃああああっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahhhhh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1333333333,
      "endTime": 58.8883220513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれ？　瑠依ちゃん？　優ちゃん？\n今日は夜までお仕事じゃなかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Oh! Rui-chan? Yu-chan?\nDidn’t you have work until late today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1,
      "endTime": 64.9264923782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "忘れ物を取りに来たんよ\nそれよりケーキ焼いたんやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I forgot something and came back to fetch it.\nWere you baking a cake?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1333333333,
      "endTime": 70.0181829484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん、そうなんだ\nたまにはお菓子作りに挑戦してみようかと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Erm‚ yes‚ I was.\nI just happened to think of giving it a try.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2333333333,
      "endTime": 76.8202748556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれが作ったケーキ、食べてみたいわね\n少しもらってもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d like to try the cake Sumire baked.\nCan I have some of it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77,
      "endTime": 82.24229421049999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "絶対ダメ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! No way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4333333333,
      "endTime": 83.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは……私が一人で食べるために作ったの！\nだからあげられないの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I made this so I can eat the whole thing by myself!\nThat’s why I can’t give you any!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7666666667,
      "endTime": 90.48432171939999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ホールケーキを一人で食べるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re going to eat the whole thing by yourself?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7,
      "endTime": 93.5394785404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "今日はケーキを沢山食べたい気分なんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just happen to fancy eating a lot of cake today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7333333333,
      "endTime": 96.8778004964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、優？\nすみれの様子がおかしいんだけど、どうしたのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Erm‚ Yu?\nSumire-chan is acting weird. I wonder what’s up with her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0666666667,
      "endTime": 102.6595699657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "はは～ん、なんとなく分かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I figured it out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8666666667,
      "endTime": 106.9148525397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "それより二人とも早く仕事に行った方がいいよ！\n遅刻するよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be better if you went to work right now!\nYou’re going to be late!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1,
      "endTime": 112.3603400844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "せやな。瑠依ちゃん、そろそろ行こか\nもたもたしとったらほんまに遅刻するわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True. We should be going‚ Rui-chan.\nIf we dawdle‚ we really will be late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6666666667,
      "endTime": 119.02411662200001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか釈然としないけど、仕方ないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I need an explanation‚ but time’s ticking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2666666667,
      "endTime": 123.2365759055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、うちらはもう行くわ\nケーキ作り頑張りや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚ we’re heading out now.\nGood luck with the cake-making.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.4333333333,
      "endTime": 128.2144163681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん、行ってらっしゃ～い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ see you later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4,
      "endTime": 132,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2299.9999999999827
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、びっくりした\nクリスマスケーキの練習だってばれてないよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what a shock!\nDid they guess that I was practicing baking a Christmas cake?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3666666667,
      "endTime": 140.2666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ところですみれちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Sumire-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.4666666667,
      "endTime": 142.113741533,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃああああっ！\nな、なに？　どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahhhhh!\nWhat? What happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3,
      "endTime": 145.9124489815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "美味しいケーキの作り方なら\nリズノワの葵ちゃんに聞いてみたらええよ",
